// Lifelink is composite-given(damage-result-rewrite) — it has no honest
// expansion until that stage exists [CR#702.15,120.3], so the composite
// carries the name alone and the engine's combat-damage hook matches it by
// name (the look-through seam, `has_keyword_named`). The
// wither/infect/toxic family shares the pending primitive.
KeywordAbility(
    name: "Lifelink",
    template: "lifelink",
    abilities: [],
)
